reviewText: I wish I had never ordered this movie, terrible
Always wanted this movie.  So glad to finally be able to get it.  Now I can watch my favourite movie/tv star, Robert Wagner in this great movie.
Good murder mystery and Robert Wagner at his best. Very suspenseful for a older movie but a good one for sure.

This  made  for  tv movie  had an excellent  cat. It included the  late Greg Morris of Mission Impossible and the late Robert Lansing.
I think that  the  idea is  a variation of  an older movie that  starred  Richard Widmark-Panic in the Streets. I found  this  movie to be entertaining and would highly recommend it.
